data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! $100,000 in UPGRADES! This beautiful unique home located in SW Cape Coral near Sands Blvd. This 3 Bedroom, 2 1/2 Bathroom pool home has a large living area with dining room. The eat in kitchen has custom cabinets, stainless steel appliances and granite counter tops. You can even have a sitting room in the kitchen area as well. The entire house has plantation shutters on all windows. The large newly tiled master suite has two walk-in closets and a large two vanity master bath. Relax in your newly fenced back yard oasis with a new pool cage with doggie door. Add an outdoor kitchen on newly extended paved lanai and take a dip into your newly resurfaced heated pool. The driveway and walkway are also newly paved, and a new metal roof was put on in 2023.
